title: 40 for 40: Early Bowls and Cheap Insect Protein
description:
Holly, Jason, Ryan, and Spencer speedrun the early slate of bowls, including answering important questions like:
1.      Which sponsors can be milled into a #nutritious #paste?
2.      Why is Pac-12 champion BYU playing UAB in Shreveport?
3.      What bowl game matchup sounds most like a super racist Supreme Court case?
4.      Will San Diego State win despite a determination to do absolutely nothing but punt? 
5.      Gasparilla Bowl? (SOURCE????)
